window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After the harrowing events of a fateful encounter with the very best of the Dominion wizards and psionicists, the Goddess Samantha and her realm must deal with the fallout. Souls, as always.<br> <br> A prisoner of Heaven; a new rival and questionable ally; a runaway with intimate and sensitive knowledge. Every encounter holds echoes of Lives Before, and each echoes again to awaken the greater forces stirring deep within them all.<br> <br> The keys to unlock a new era continue to fall into her hands. <b>But can this heroine find the right doors to open?</b></p>"; 
